data.eml:eml: Five new Mallinella species from the Sundaland of Indonesia (Araneae, Zodariidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Dankittipakul, Pakawin, Jocqué, Rudy, Singtripop, Tippawan (2010): Five new Mallinella species from the Sundaland of Indonesia (Araneae, Zodariidae). Zootaxa 2636: 21-36, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.276153
